'''1864年大西洋飓风季'''是19世纪60年代连续第三个没有飓风[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]美国的[[大西洋飓风季|大西洋飓风季]]，这项纪录至今依然保持<ref name="u.s. hurricanes">{{cite report | title = Chronological List of All Hurricanes: 1851 – 2012 | date = 2013 | work = Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory | archivedate = 2016-11-13 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161113005842/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/All_U.S._Hurricanes.html | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2016-11-25 | location = Miami, Florida | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/All_U.S._Hurricanes.html }}</ref>。不过，考虑到当时缺乏包括气象卫星在内的现代观测手段，基本上只有那些在海上遇到船只或是吹袭有人类居住陆地的风暴才有文献记载，所以实际形成的热带气旋可能更多。[[气象学|气象学家]][[克里斯托弗·朗诗|克里斯托弗·朗诗]]（{{lang|en|Christopher W. Landsea}}）估计，1851至1885年间实际形成的风暴数量可能比数据库中要多零到六场。<ref>{{cite book | title = Hurricanes and Typhoons: Past, Present and Future | chapter = The Atlantic hurricane database re-analysis project: Documentation for the 1851–1910 alterations and additions to the HURDAT database | author = Christopher W. Landsea | year = 2004 | publisher = Columbia University Press | isbn = 0-231-12388-4 | pages = 177–221}}</ref>全季确认存在的五个北大西洋热带气旋中有四个是由气象学家何塞·费尔南德斯-帕塔加斯（{{lang|en|Jose Fernandez-Partagas}}）和亨利·迪亚兹（{{lang|en|Henry Diaz}}）在1995年出版的文献中首度记载<ref name="partagas-1">{{cite book | author1 = Jose Fernández-Partagás | author2 = Henry F. Diaz | title = A Reconstruction of Historical Tropical Cyclone Frequency in the Atlantic from Documentary and other Historical Sources 1851-1880 Part 1: 1851-1870 | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/Landsea/Partagas/part1.htm | publisher = Climate Diagnostics Center, National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304204604/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/Landsea/Partagas/part1.htm | work = Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory | location = Boulder, Colorado | year = 1995 | accessdate = 2016-11-25 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。7月16日，本季第一个天气系统在[[美国东南部|美国东南部]]近海出现，其最高强度可以在现代[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下达到一级飓风标准{{#tag:ref|[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]于1971年面世<ref name="USA Today">{{cite news | author = Jack Williams | title = Hurricane scale invented to communicate storm danger | publisher = [[今日美国|USA Today]] | date = 2005-05-17 | accessdate = 2013-08-04 | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/hurricane/whscale.htm | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160324154907/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/hurricane/whscale.htm | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-24 }}</ref>，再对[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]大西洋飓风数据库的所有风暴追溯分级<ref>{{cite report | publisher = Hurricane Research Division | title = Chronological List of All Continental United States Hurricanes: 1851-2012 | date = 2013-06 | accessdate = 2016-11-10 | archivedate = 2016-05-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160503012801/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/All_U.S._Hurricanes.html | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/All_U.S._Hurricanes.html }}</ref>。|group="注"}}。气旋快速向东北移动，于7月18日从[[纽芬兰岛|纽芬兰岛]]以东较远处洋面经过后失去踪影。

7月25日，第二场风暴在[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]中南部出现，但只能确认气旋曾在某位置经过，详细移动路线和强弱变化均已无从考证。经过一个多月的沉寂，[[小安的列斯群岛|小安的列斯群岛]]东侧海域于8月26日形成另一场飓风。次日清晨，风暴从[[多米尼克|多米尼克]]和[[马提尼克|马提尼克]]之间穿过。经过[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]后，气旋于8月31日晚登陆[[伯利兹|伯利兹]]，最终于次日逐渐消散。伯利兹近海有多艘船只遭遇风暴，沿海部分地区被[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]淹没。9月5至9日，第四号热带风暴在[[美国东岸|美国东岸]]近海活动，多艘船只在行进至气旋附近时遭遇强风。第五个热带气旋也出现在美国东岸近海，许多船只遇到强烈雷暴和恶劣海况。

这年飓风季的活跃程度还经累积[[气旋能量指数|气旋能量指数]]反映出来，数值为61<ref name="ACE">{{cite report | author = Hurricane Research Division | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2011-03 | title = Atlantic basin Comparison of Original and Revised HURDAT | accessdate = 2016-03-04 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304040342/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/Comparison_of_Original_and_Revised_HURDAT_mar11.html | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/Comparison_of_Original_and_Revised_HURDAT_mar11.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。大致来说，气旋能量指数通过飓风强度和持续时间计算，强度越高、持续时间越长的风暴，其指数也相应越高。只有在热带天气系统风速达到或超过每小时63公里（34[[节_(单位)|节]]）或热带风暴强度时才会计算该指数，并纳入全面的气象公告，并且[[亚热带气旋|亚热带气旋]]的指数不会计入累积数值。<ref>{{cite web |author=David Levinson |date=2008-08-20 |title=2005 Atlantic Ocean Tropical Cyclones |publisher=National Climatic Data Center |archiveurl=https://archive.li/20131105020723/http://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/oa/climate/research/2005/2005-atlantic-trop-cyclones.html |archivedate=2013-11-05 |deadurl=no |accessdate=2014-04-01 |url=http://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/oa/climate/research/2005/2005-atlantic-trop-cyclones.html }}</ref>
