7月16日，“哈蒂·伊顿号”（{{lang|en|Hattie Eaton}}）[[三桅帆船|三桅帆船]]在距[[南卡罗莱纳州|南]]、[[北卡莱纳州|北卡莱纳州]]数百英里海域发现本季第一个[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]，船上所测持续风速为每小时130公里，在现代[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下属一级飓风标准<ref name="partagas-1" />。7月18日清晨，气旋减弱成热带风暴。“能源号”（{{lang|en|Energy}}）船只于数小时后在[[纽芬兰岛|纽芬兰岛]][[开普雷斯|开普雷斯]]（{{lang|en|Cape Race}}）以东约700公里洋面遇到这场风暴，此后气旋便失去踪影。<ref name="partagas-1" /><ref name="HURDAT">{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | title = Atlantic hurricane best track (HURDAT version 2) | accessdate = 2016-11-01 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2016-07-06 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-10-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161004150702/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | format = [[文本文件|TXT]] }}</ref>
{{Clear}}

